description: Permascand Top Holding AB is a SE-based company operating in  industry. Permascand Top Holding AB is a Sweden-based high-tech manufacturer of electrochemical solutions based on catalytic coatings - for environmental engineering applications. The firm has a range of engineering and manufacturing offers based on our Core Product Platform that spans catalytic coatings, electrodes, and electrochemical cells to coating and aftermarket services. Permascand Top Holding operates through three business segments: Electrification & Renewables, Industrial solutions and Water treatment.
